channel.description:
[IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/minrdg.jpg[/img]
Alright so I hosted this server EliteProdigyz for a bit. I think I'm going to Release it why not. You can say I leeched it. But to bad I don't give a fuck. Alrighty :). I'll tell you the server I used. So Flame me if you want :D. (AGAIN IDGAF! :D) Its my [size=14pt]First Release[/size] so don't flame me please.
First off. [size=12pt]CREDITS FOR U NUBBBBS <3[/size] (Got these off the source I used. Edited em I bit. NO PERCENTS YAY.) Shane aka me for home and other [size=14pt]LITTLE STUFF[/size] hyBriDPvP - Source (Gave me got off him. Idk what he/she did.) 2012 - For the Trade Interface Kr4n4ge - 634 Models Penor - 508 Maps D3mons Dead - Dung Cape Emote Ninja assassin - For helping me fixing stuff C0re - Started with his client + source, Thats why i didnt rename the client its still his client - I added 634 Items and Lunar Interface + Trade Interface. Ninja assassin Fixed Model.java
Alright time for Features.. [size=18pt]Features[/size]
Dung Armor!
Pvp Armor!
Varrock 602 Home!
All Skills work except for Agility! (From what I know..)
100% Skillcape Emotes! (Includes Dung)
Easy Eco (Aka Cheap Prices.)
Great Pking!
Custom STAFFZONE!
CUSTOM JAIL! - (I liked so creds who made :D)
Theiving! (Yay cause exp rates and money failed :P (FIXED) )
Claws 100% of course ;D
Chaotics!
Mini-games 100% (With a Custom mini-game Battle Grounds!)
Fixed Prayer Altar! - Me.
Woo... Alot more stuff.. Btw server has 508-602 Features!
Pictures. (Hoping Imagines work :S.

I think thats about it! All talk about what I changed below with Download Links.
Downloads: Uppit :) (If the client says it has a virus it dosent. I wouldnt give out a client with a virus and a server with not. It's your choice to download... It just has been reported that it says it does.)
Client: http://up.ht/gTszjn Mirror2: http://uppit.com/18j5a2pm099m/Your_Client.zip Server: http://up.ht/hhPxgP Mirror2: http://uppit.com/idx3tqs70fcn/Your_Server.zip
Other Info...
Alright I did use the source Pvp Hybrid. To Edit not intended to leech. I hosted it for a while week or 2. We just couldnt get up and running, So me and my co-owner: Wanted. Said farewell we had a 'terrible' run. Which we did which is funny in a way. I also quit because I'm gonna bot on my hosting comp. So don't want it to laggy for my members. So now I'm here with a source and client. ( I DONT OWN THE SOURCE OR CLIENT.)
Now for all you crazy leech people. I didn't leech this. I like to say I "edited it" Don't quote me on this. You can call this leech if you want. But I could care less. I think I did a good job on my first release. (Maybe my only :|) So please don't leave nasty, dirty comments cause your just wasting your time. I will only reply to the good ones not the messed up ones.
- OmgItsShane
